snippet.title: 'Round The World - CGS 2021
snippet.description:
MiKe is a teenager who wakes up in a room with a few old TVs near him. In these TVs, the news say that he is being bountied upwards of 10,000 fethlers after having commited several criminal activities. He runs off to the nearest train station, planning to stop at the place he remembers wanting to go last, the Axolotl Central Park, a theme park city on top of a floating island.


Check the game as soon as the 18th hits!
